59    protected function writeDrawingRelations(AbstractSlideAlias $pSlideMaster, XMLWriter $objWriter, int $relId)
60    {
61        if ($pSlideMaster->getShapeCollection()->count() > 0) {
62            // Loop trough images and write relationships
63            $iterator = $pSlideMaster->getShapeCollection()->getIterator();
64            while ($iterator->valid()) {
65                if ($iterator->current() instanceof ShapeDrawingFile || $iterator->current() instanceof ShapeDrawingGd) {
66                    // Write relationship for image drawing
67                    $this->writeRelationship(
68                        $objWriter,
69                        $relId,
70                        'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/image',
71                        '../media/' . str_replace(' ', '_', $iterator->current()->getIndexedFilename())
72                    );
73                    $iterator->current()->relationId = 'rId' . $relId;
74                    ++$relId;
75                } elseif ($iterator->current() instanceof ShapeChart) {
76                    // Write relationship for chart drawing
77                    $this->writeRelationship(
78                        $objWriter,
79                        $relId,
80                        'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/chart',
81                        '../charts/' . $iterator->current()->getIndexedFilename()
82                    );
83                    $iterator->current()->relationId = 'rId' . $relId;
84                    ++$relId;
85                } elseif ($iterator->current() instanceof Group) {
86                    $iterator2 = $iterator->current()->getShapeCollection()->getIterator();
87                    while ($iterator2->valid()) {
88                        if ($iterator2->current() instanceof ShapeDrawingFile ||
89                            $iterator2->current() instanceof ShapeDrawingGd
90                        ) {
91                            // Write relationship for image drawing
92                            $this->writeRelationship(
93                                $objWriter,
94                                $relId,
95                                'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/image',
96                                '../media/' . str_replace(' ', '_', $iterator2->current()->getIndexedFilename())
97                            );
98                            $iterator2->current()->relationId = 'rId' . $relId;
99                            ++$relId;
100                        } elseif ($iterator2->current() instanceof ShapeChart) {
101                            // Write relationship for chart drawing
102                            $this->writeRelationship(
103                                $objWriter,
104                                $relId,
105                                'http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/chart',
106                                '../charts/' . $iterator2->current()->getIndexedFilename()
107                            );
108                            $iterator2->current()->relationId = 'rId' . $relId;
109                            ++$relId;
110                        }
111                        $iterator2->next();
112                    }
113                }
114                $iterator->next();
115            }
116        }
117
118        return $relId;
119    }

121    /**
122     * Note : $shapeId needs to start to 1
123     *  The animation is applied to the shape which is next to the target shape.
124     *
125     * @param array<int, AbstractShape>|ArrayObject<int, AbstractShape> $shapes
126     * @param int $shapeId
127     */
128    protected function writeShapeCollection(XMLWriter $objWriter, $shapes = [], &$shapeId = 1): void
129    {
130        if (0 == count($shapes)) {
131            return;
132        }
133        foreach ($shapes as $shape) {
134            // Increment $shapeId
135            ++$shapeId;
136            // Check type
137            if ($shape instanceof RichText) {
138                $this->writeShapeText($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
139            } elseif ($shape instanceof ShapeTable) {
140                $this->writeShapeTable($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
141            } elseif ($shape instanceof Line) {
142                $this->writeShapeLine($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
143            } elseif ($shape instanceof ShapeChart) {
144                $this->writeShapeChart($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
145            } elseif ($shape instanceof AbstractGraphic) {
146                $this->writeShapePic($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
147            } elseif ($shape instanceof AutoShape) {
148                $this->writeShapeAutoShape($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
149            } elseif ($shape instanceof Group) {
150                $this->writeShapeGroup($objWriter, $shape, $shapeId);
151            } elseif ($shape instanceof Comment) {
152            } else {
153                throw new UndefinedChartTypeException();
154            }
155        }
156    }

158    /**
159     * Write txt.
160     *
161     * @param XMLWriter $objWriter XML Writer
162     */
163    protected function writeShapeText(XMLWriter $objWriter, RichText $shape, int $shapeId): void
164    {
165        // p:sp
166        $objWriter->startElement('p:sp');
167        // p:sp\p:nvSpPr
168        $objWriter->startElement('p:nvSpPr');
169        // p:sp\p:nvSpPr\p:cNvPr
170        $objWriter->startElement('p:cNvPr');
171        $objWriter->writeAttribute('id', $shapeId);
172        if ($shape->isPlaceholder()) {
173            $objWriter->writeAttribute('name', 'Placeholder for ' . $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType());
174        } else {
175            $objWriter->writeAttribute('name', '');
176        }
177        // Hyperlink
178        if ($shape->hasHyperlink()) {
179            $this->writeHyperlink($objWriter, $shape);
180        }
181        // > p:sp\p:nvSpPr
182        $objWriter->endElement();
183        // p:sp\p:nvSpPr\p:cNvSpPr
184        $objWriter->startElement('p:cNvSpPr');
185        $objWriter->writeAttribute('txBox', '1');
186        $objWriter->endElement();
187        // p:sp\p:nvSpPr\p:nvPr
188        if ($shape->isPlaceholder()) {
189            $objWriter->startElement('p:nvPr');
190            $objWriter->startElement('p:ph');
191            $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType());
192            if (null !== $shape->getPlaceholder()->getIdx()) {
193                $objWriter->writeAttribute('idx', $shape->getPlaceholder()->getIdx());
194            }
195            $objWriter->endElement();
196            $objWriter->endElement();
197        } else {
198            $objWriter->writeElement('p:nvPr', null);
199        }
200        // > p:sp\p:nvSpPr
201        $objWriter->endElement();
202        // p:sp\p:spPr
203        $objWriter->startElement('p:spPr');
204
205        // p:sp\p:spPr\a:xfrm
206        $objWriter->startElement('a:xfrm');
207        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($shape->getRotation() != 0, 'rot', CommonDrawing::degreesToAngle($shape->getRotation()));
208        // p:sp\p:spPr\a:xfrm\a:off
209        $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
210        $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX()));
211        $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY()));
212        $objWriter->endElement();
213        // p:sp\p:spPr\a:xfrm\a:ext
214        $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
215        $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getWidth()));
216        $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getHeight()));
217        $objWriter->endElement();
218        // > p:sp\p:spPr\a:xfrm
219        $objWriter->endElement();
220        // p:sp\p:spPr\a:prstGeom
221        $objWriter->startElement('a:prstGeom');
222        $objWriter->writeAttribute('prst', 'rect');
223
224        // p:sp\p:spPr\a:prstGeom\a:avLst
225        $objWriter->writeElement('a:avLst');
226
227        $objWriter->endElement();
228
229        $this->writeFill($objWriter, $shape->getFill());
230        $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $shape->getBorder(), '');
231        $this->writeShadow($objWriter, $shape->getShadow());
232
233        // > p:sp\p:spPr
234        $objWriter->endElement();
235        // p:txBody
236        $objWriter->startElement('p:txBody');
237        // a:bodyPr
238        //@link :http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/documentformat.openxml.drawing.bodyproperties%28v=office.14%29.aspx
239        $objWriter->startElement('a:bodyPr');
240        if (!$shape->isPlaceholder()) {
241            $verticalAlign = $shape->getActiveParagraph()->getAlignment()->getVertical();
242            if (Alignment::VERTICAL_BASE != $verticalAlign && Alignment::VERTICAL_AUTO != $verticalAlign) {
243                $objWriter->writeAttribute('anchor', $verticalAlign);
244            }
245            if (RichText::WRAP_SQUARE != $shape->getWrap()) {
246                $objWriter->writeAttribute('wrap', $shape->getWrap());
247            }
248            $objWriter->writeAttribute('rtlCol', '0');
249            if (RichText::OVERFLOW_OVERFLOW != $shape->getHorizontalOverflow()) {
250                $objWriter->writeAttribute('horzOverflow', $shape->getHorizontalOverflow());
251            }
252            if (RichText::OVERFLOW_OVERFLOW != $shape->getVerticalOverflow()) {
253                $objWriter->writeAttribute('vertOverflow', $shape->getVerticalOverflow());
254            }
255            if ($shape->isUpright()) {
256                $objWriter->writeAttribute('upright', '1');
257            }
258            if ($shape->isVertical()) {
259                $objWriter->writeAttribute('vert', 'vert');
260            }
261            $objWriter->writeAttribute('bIns', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getInsetBottom()));
262            $objWriter->writeAttribute('lIns', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getInsetLeft()));
263            $objWriter->writeAttribute('rIns', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getInsetRight()));
264            $objWriter->writeAttribute('tIns', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getInsetTop()));
265            if (1 != $shape->getColumns()) {
266                $objWriter->writeAttribute('numCol', $shape->getColumns());
267                $objWriter->writeAttribute('spcCol', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getColumnSpacing()));
268            }
269            // a:spAutoFit
270            $objWriter->startElement('a:' . $shape->getAutoFit());
271            if (RichText::AUTOFIT_NORMAL == $shape->getAutoFit()) {
272                if (null !== $shape->getFontScale()) {
273                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('fontScale', $shape->getFontScale() * 1000);
274                }
275                if (null !== $shape->getLineSpaceReduction()) {
276                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('lnSpcReduction', $shape->getLineSpaceReduction() * 1000);
277                }
278            }
279            $objWriter->endElement();
280        }
281        $objWriter->endElement();
282        // a:lstStyle
283        $objWriter->writeElement('a:lstStyle', null);
284        if ($shape->isPlaceholder() &&
285            (Placeholder::PH_TYPE_SLIDENUM == $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType() ||
286                Placeholder::PH_TYPE_DATETIME == $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType())
287        ) {
288            $objWriter->startElement('a:p');
289
290            // Paragraph Style
291            $paragraphs = $shape->getParagraphs();
292            if (!empty($paragraphs)) {
293                $paragraph = &$paragraphs[0];
294                $this->writeParagraphStyles($objWriter, $paragraph, true);
295            }
296
297            $objWriter->startElement('a:fld');
298            $objWriter->writeAttribute('id', $this->getGUID());
299            $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', (
300                Placeholder::PH_TYPE_SLIDENUM == $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType() ? 'slidenum' : 'datetime'
301            ));
302
303            if (isset($paragraph)) {
304                $elements = $paragraph->getRichTextElements();
305                if (!empty($elements)) {
306                    $element = &$elements[0];
307                    if ($element instanceof Run) {
308                        $this->writeRunStyles($objWriter, $element);
309                    }
310                }
311            }
312
313            $objWriter->writeElement('a:t', (
314                Placeholder::PH_TYPE_SLIDENUM == $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType() ? '<nr.>' : '03-04-05'
315            ));
316            $objWriter->endElement();
317            $objWriter->endElement();
318        } else {
319            // Write paragraphs
320            $this->writeParagraphs($objWriter, $shape->getParagraphs());
321        }
322        $objWriter->endElement();
323        $objWriter->endElement();
324    }

384        $objWriter->writeAttribute('firstRow', '1');
385        $objWriter->writeAttribute('bandRow', '1');
386        $objWriter->endElement();
387        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tblGrid
388        $objWriter->startElement('a:tblGrid');
389        // Write cell widths
390        $countCells = count($shape->getRow(0)->getCells());
391        for ($cell = 0; $cell < $countCells; ++$cell) {
392            //  p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tblGrid/a:gridCol
393            $objWriter->startElement('a:gridCol');
394            // Calculate column width
395            $width = $shape->getRow(0)->getCell($cell)->getWidth();
396            if (0 == $width) {
397                $colCount = count($shape->getRow(0)->getCells());
398                $totalWidth = $shape->getWidth();
399                $width = $totalWidth / $colCount;
400            }
401            $objWriter->writeAttribute('w', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($width));
402            $objWriter->endElement();
403        }
404        // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tblGrid/
405        $objWriter->endElement();
406        // Colspan / rowspan containers
407        $colSpan = $rowSpan = [];
408        // Default border style
409        $defaultBorder = new Border();
410        // Write rows
411        $countRows = count($shape->getRows());
412        for ($row = 0; $row < $countRows; ++$row) {
413            // p:graphicFrame/a:graphic/a:graphicData/a:tbl/a:tr
414            $objWriter->startElement('a:tr');
415            $objWriter->writeAttribute('h', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getRow($row)->getHeight()));
416            // Write cells
417            $countCells = count($shape->getRow($row)->getCells());
418            for ($cell = 0; $cell < $countCells; ++$cell) {
419                // Current cell
420                $currentCell = $shape->getRow($row)->getCell($cell);
421                // Next cell right
422                $hasNextCellRight = $shape->getRow($row)->hasCell($cell + 1);
423                // Next cell below
424                $hasNextRowBelow = $shape->hasRow($row + 1);
425                // a:tc
426                $objWriter->startElement('a:tc');
427                // Colspan
428                if ($currentCell->getColSpan() > 1) {
429                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('gridSpan', $currentCell->getColSpan());
430                    $colSpan[$row] = $currentCell->getColSpan() - 1;
431                } elseif (isset($colSpan[$row]) && $colSpan[$row] > 0) {
432                    --$colSpan[$row];
433                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('hMerge', '1');
434                }
435                // Rowspan
436                if ($currentCell->getRowSpan() > 1) {
437                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('rowSpan', $currentCell->getRowSpan());
438                    $rowSpan[$cell] = $currentCell->getRowSpan() - 1;
439                } elseif (isset($rowSpan[$cell]) && $rowSpan[$cell] > 0) {
440                    --$rowSpan[$cell];
441                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('vMerge', '1');
442                }
443                // a:txBody
444                $objWriter->startElement('a:txBody');
445                // a:txBody/a:bodyPr
446                $objWriter->startElement('a:bodyPr');
447                $objWriter->writeAttribute('wrap', 'square');
448                $objWriter->writeAttribute('rtlCol', '0');
449                // a:txBody/a:bodyPr/a:spAutoFit
450                $objWriter->writeElement('a:spAutoFit', null);
451                // a:txBody/a:bodyPr/
452                $objWriter->endElement();
453                // a:lstStyle
454                $objWriter->writeElement('a:lstStyle', null);
455                // Write paragraphs
456                $this->writeParagraphs($objWriter, $currentCell->getParagraphs());
457                $objWriter->endElement();
458                // a:tcPr
459                $objWriter->startElement('a:tcPr');
460                $firstParagraph = $currentCell->getParagraph(0);
461                $firstParagraphAlignment = $firstParagraph->getAlignment();
462
463                // Text Direction
464                $textDirection = $firstParagraphAlignment->getTextDirection();
465                if (Alignment::TEXT_DIRECTION_HORIZONTAL != $textDirection) {
466                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('vert', $textDirection);
467                }
468                // Alignment (horizontal)
469                $verticalAlign = $firstParagraphAlignment->getVertical();
470                if (Alignment::VERTICAL_BASE != $verticalAlign && Alignment::VERTICAL_AUTO != $verticalAlign) {
471                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('anchor', $verticalAlign);
472                }
473
474                // Margins
475                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marL', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($firstParagraphAlignment->getMarginLeft()));
476                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marR', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($firstParagraphAlignment->getMarginRight()));
477                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marT', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($firstParagraphAlignment->getMarginTop()));
478                $objWriter->writeAttribute('marB', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($firstParagraphAlignment->getMarginBottom()));
479
480                // Determine borders
481                $borderLeft = $currentCell->getBorders()->getLeft();
482                $borderRight = $currentCell->getBorders()->getRight();
483                $borderTop = $currentCell->getBorders()->getTop();
484                $borderBottom = $currentCell->getBorders()->getBottom();
485                $borderDiagonalDown = $currentCell->getBorders()->getDiagonalDown();
486                $borderDiagonalUp = $currentCell->getBorders()->getDiagonalUp();
487                // Fix PowerPoint implementation
488                if ($hasNextCellRight) {
489                    $nextCellRight = $shape->getRow($row)->getCell($cell + 1);
490                    if ($nextCellRight->getBorders()->getRight()->getHashCode() != $defaultBorder->getHashCode()) {
491                        $borderRight = $nextCellRight->getBorders()->getLeft();
492                    }
493                }
494                if ($hasNextRowBelow) {
495                    $nextRowBelow = $shape->getRow($row + 1);
496                    $nextCellBelow = $nextRowBelow->getCell($cell);
497                    if ($nextCellBelow->getBorders()->getBottom()->getHashCode() != $defaultBorder->getHashCode()) {
498                        $borderBottom = $nextCellBelow->getBorders()->getTop();
499                    }
500                }
501                // Write borders
502                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderLeft, 'L');
503                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderRight, 'R');
504                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderTop, 'T');
505                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderBottom, 'B');
506                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderDiagonalDown, 'TlToBr');
507                $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $borderDiagonalUp, 'BlToTr');
508                // Fill
509                $this->writeFill($objWriter, $currentCell->getFill());
510                $objWriter->endElement();
511                $objWriter->endElement();
512            }
513            $objWriter->endElement();
514        }
515        $objWriter->endElement();
516        $objWriter->endElement();
517        $objWriter->endElement();
518        $objWriter->endElement();
519    }
520
521    /**
522     * Write paragraphs.
523     *
524     * @param XMLWriter $objWriter XML Writer
525     * @param array<Paragraph> $paragraphs
526     */
527    protected function writeParagraphs(XMLWriter $objWriter, array $paragraphs): void
528    {
529        // Loop trough paragraphs
530        foreach ($paragraphs as $paragraph) {
531            // a:p
532            $objWriter->startElement('a:p');
533
534            // a:pPr
535            $this->writeParagraphStyles($objWriter, $paragraph, false);
536
537            // Loop trough rich text elements
538            $elements = $paragraph->getRichTextElements();
539            foreach ($elements as $element) {
540                if ($element instanceof BreakElement) {
541                    // a:br
542                    $objWriter->writeElement('a:br', null);
543                } elseif ($element instanceof Run || $element instanceof TextElement) {
544                    // a:r
545                    $objWriter->startElement('a:r');
546
547                    // a:rPr
548                    if ($element instanceof Run) {
549                        $this->writeRunStyles($objWriter, $element);
550                    }
551
552                    // t
553                    $objWriter->startElement('a:t');
554                    $objWriter->writeCData(Text::controlCharacterPHP2OOXML($element->getText()));
555                    $objWriter->endElement();
556
557                    $objWriter->endElement();
558                }
559            }
560
561            $objWriter->endElement();
562        }
563    }
564
565    /**
566     * Write Paragraph Styles (a:pPr).
567     */
568    protected function writeParagraphStyles(XMLWriter $objWriter, RichText\Paragraph $paragraph, bool $isPlaceholder = false): void
569    {
570        $objWriter->startElement('a:pPr');
571        $objWriter->writeAttribute('algn', $paragraph->getAlignment()->getHorizontal());
572        $objWriter->writeAttribute('rtl', $paragraph->getAlignment()->isRTL() ? '1' : '0');
573        $objWriter->writeAttribute('fontAlgn', $paragraph->getAlignment()->getVertical());
574        $objWriter->writeAttribute('marL', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($paragraph->getAlignment()->getMarginLeft()));
575        $objWriter->writeAttribute('marR', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($paragraph->getAlignment()->getMarginRight()));
576        $objWriter->writeAttribute('indent', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($paragraph->getAlignment()->getIndent()));
577        $objWriter->writeAttribute('lvl', $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel());
578
579        $objWriter->startElement('a:lnSpc');
580        if ($paragraph->getLineSpacingMode() == Paragraph::LINE_SPACING_MODE_POINT) {
581            $objWriter->startElement('a:spcPts');
582            $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', $paragraph->getLineSpacing() * 100);
583            $objWriter->endElement();
584        } else {
585            $objWriter->startElement('a:spcPct');
586            $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', $paragraph->getLineSpacing() * 1000);
587            $objWriter->endElement();
588        }
589        $objWriter->endElement();
590
591        $objWriter->startElement('a:spcBef');
592        $objWriter->startElement('a:spcPts');
593        $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', $paragraph->getSpacingBefore() * 100);
594        $objWriter->endElement();
595        $objWriter->endElement();
596
597        $objWriter->startElement('a:spcAft');
598        $objWriter->startElement('a:spcPts');
599        $objWriter->writeAttribute('val', $paragraph->getSpacingAfter() * 100);
600        $objWriter->endElement();
601        $objWriter->endElement();
602
603        if (!$isPlaceholder) {
604            // Bullet type specified?
605            if ($paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType() != Bullet::TYPE_NONE) {
606                // Color
607                // a:buClr must be before a:buFont (else PowerPoint crashes at launch)
608                if ($paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletColor() instanceof Color) {
609                    $objWriter->startElement('a:buClr');
610                    $this->writeColor($objWriter, $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletColor());
611                    $objWriter->endElement();
612                }
613
614                // a:buFont
615                $objWriter->startElement('a:buFont');
616                $objWriter->writeAttribute('typeface', $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletFont());
617                $objWriter->endElement();
618
619                if ($paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType() == Bullet::TYPE_BULLET) {
620                    // a:buChar
621                    $objWriter->startElement('a:buChar');
622                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('char', $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletChar());
623                    $objWriter->endElement();
624                } elseif ($paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType() == Bullet::TYPE_NUMERIC) {
625                    // a:buAutoNum
626                    $objWriter->startElement('a:buAutoNum');
627                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletNumericStyle());
628                    if ($paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletNumericStartAt() != 1) {
629                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('startAt', $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletNumericStartAt());
630                    }
631                    $objWriter->endElement();
632                }
633            }
634        }
635
636        $objWriter->endElement();
637    }

639    /**
640     * Write RichTextElement Styles (a:pPr).
641     */
642    protected function writeRunStyles(XMLWriter $objWriter, RichText\Run $element): void
643    {
644        // a:rPr
645        $objWriter->startElement('a:rPr');
646
647        // Lang
648        $objWriter->writeAttribute('lang', ($element->getLanguage() ? $element->getLanguage() : 'en-US'));
649
650        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isBold(), 'b', '1');
651        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isItalic(), 'i', '1');
652        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isStrikethrough(), 'strike', 'sngStrike');
653
654        // Size
655        $objWriter->writeAttribute('sz', ($element->getFont()->getSize() * 100));
656
657        // Character spacing
658        $objWriter->writeAttribute('spc', $element->getFont()->getCharacterSpacing());
659
660        // Underline
661        $objWriter->writeAttribute('u', $element->getFont()->getUnderline());
662
663        // Capitalization
664        $objWriter->writeAttribute('cap', $element->getFont()->getCapitalization());
665
666        // Superscript / subscript
667        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isSuperScript(), 'baseline', '300000');
668        $objWriter->writeAttributeIf($element->getFont()->isSubScript(), 'baseline', '-250000');
669
670        // Color - a:solidFill
671        $objWriter->startElement('a:solidFill');
672        $this->writeColor($objWriter, $element->getFont()->getColor());
673        $objWriter->endElement();
674
675        // Font
676        // - a:latin
677        // - a:ea
678        // - a:cs
679        $objWriter->startElement('a:' . $element->getFont()->getFormat());
680        $objWriter->writeAttribute('typeface', $element->getFont()->getName());
681        $objWriter->endElement();
682
683        // a:hlinkClick
684        $this->writeHyperlink($objWriter, $element);
685
686        $objWriter->endElement();
687    }

689    /**
690     * Write Line Shape.
691     *
692     * @param XMLWriter $objWriter XML Writer
693     */
694    protected function writeShapeLine(XMLWriter $objWriter, Line $shape, int $shapeId): void
695    {
696        // p:sp
697        $objWriter->startElement('p:cxnSp');
698        // p:nvSpPr
699        $objWriter->startElement('p:nvCxnSpPr');
700        // p:cNvPr
701        $objWriter->startElement('p:cNvPr');
702        $objWriter->writeAttribute('id', $shapeId);
703        $objWriter->writeAttribute('name', '');
704        $objWriter->endElement();
705        // p:cNvCxnSpPr
706        $objWriter->writeElement('p:cNvCxnSpPr', null);
707        // p:nvPr
708        $objWriter->startElement('p:nvPr');
709        if ($shape->isPlaceholder()) {
710            $objWriter->startElement('p:ph');
711            $objWriter->writeAttribute('type', $shape->getPlaceholder()->getType());
712            $objWriter->endElement();
713        }
714        $objWriter->endElement();
715        $objWriter->endElement();
716        // p:spPr
717        $objWriter->startElement('p:spPr');
718        // a:xfrm
719        $objWriter->startElement('a:xfrm');
720        if ($shape->getWidth() >= 0 && $shape->getHeight() >= 0) {
721            // a:off
722            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
723            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX()));
724            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY()));
725            $objWriter->endElement();
726            // a:ext
727            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
728            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getWidth()));
729            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getHeight()));
730            $objWriter->endElement();
731        } elseif ($shape->getWidth() < 0 && $shape->getHeight() < 0) {
732            // a:off
733            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
734            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX() + $shape->getWidth()));
735            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY() + $shape->getHeight()));
736            $objWriter->endElement();
737            // a:ext
738            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
739            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu(-$shape->getWidth()));
740            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu(-$shape->getHeight()));
741            $objWriter->endElement();
742        } elseif ($shape->getHeight() < 0) {
743            $objWriter->writeAttribute('flipV', 1);
744            // a:off
745            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
746            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX()));
747            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY() + $shape->getHeight()));
748            $objWriter->endElement();
749            // a:ext
750            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
751            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getWidth()));
752            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu(-$shape->getHeight()));
753            $objWriter->endElement();
754        } elseif ($shape->getWidth() < 0) {
755            $objWriter->writeAttribute('flipV', 1);
756            // a:off
757            $objWriter->startElement('a:off');
758            $objWriter->writeAttribute('x', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetX() + $shape->getWidth()));
759            $objWriter->writeAttribute('y', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getOffsetY()));
760            $objWriter->endElement();
761            // a:ext
762            $objWriter->startElement('a:ext');
763            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cx', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu(-$shape->getWidth()));
764            $objWriter->writeAttribute('cy', CommonDrawing::pixelsToEmu($shape->getHeight()));
765            $objWriter->endElement();
766        }
767        $objWriter->endElement();
768        // a:prstGeom
769        $objWriter->startElement('a:prstGeom');
770        $objWriter->writeAttribute('prst', 'line');
771
772        // a:prstGeom/a:avLst
773        $objWriter->writeElement('a:avLst');
774
775        $objWriter->endElement();
776        $this->writeBorder($objWriter, $shape->getBorder(), '');
777        $objWriter->endElement();
778        $objWriter->endElement();
779    }

782     * Write Shadow.
783     */
784    protected function writeShadow(XMLWriter $objWriter, Shadow $oShadow): void

834            $objWriter->endElement();
835            $objWriter->endElement();
836            $objWriter->endElement();
837        }
838
839        $objWriter->endElement();
840    }

842    /**
843     * Write Note Slide.
844     */
845    protected function writeNote(Note $pNote): string
846    {
847        // Create XML writer
848        $objWriter = new XMLWriter(XMLWriter::STORAGE_MEMORY);
